I’m very disappointed in ETUDE. 

As the #14 Rose Lilac is an Olive Young exclusive, if I want it I have to buy it there— except Olive Young doesn’t do DDP (Delivery Duty Paid), meaning that as a European citizen I have to pay custom duties & fees. Before summer 2021 there was a law that exempted small purchases under €22 from VAT/custom fees, except that law has been changed. So now a $16 Tint turns into a ~$40 tint (20% tax + $21 application fee) + shipping. Great. 

Usually I don’t have any problems since I buy from Korean beauty shops in Europe, but in this case it’s impossible as it’s an Olive Young exclusive. Even though I wanna give them my money, I don’t wanna pay double (especially for taxes). 

Damn the color is so pretty too… and I’m winter cool… damn you ETUDE
